cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about speech recognition and language modeling. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with acoustic signals. 
- cs.SI (Signal Processing) is another possible category as the paper discusses techniques to mitigate the issue of requiring more data to train reliably. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses connectionist temporal classification (CTC) loss to convert acoustics to word sequences. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper presents an end-to-end automatic speech recognition system.
